displayName: Golden City of Dromos, Residential House 1F

parameters: Wealthy Daughter: Do you need something?

Wealthy Daughter: I wonder if you would like to hear about
my father's work. You see, I am entrusted with the sale of
some crystals...

Wealthy Daughter: I've been targeted multiple times... I
will try to persuade you. Thank you for listening.

Wealthy Daughter: This lifestyle is thanks to the
sacrifices of my father... I will also live in a way that
can contribute to my father's strength.
